  "name": "Morrison COU2 — VAD hemolysis credibility assessment (COMPOUND-03 adversarial)",
  "description": "V&V 40 credibility assessment for CFD hemolysis prediction of the FDA generic centrifugal blood pump under ventricular assist device (VAD) conditions. COU2 evaluates whether the computational model can predict absolute hemolysis levels for a Class III VAD device at Model Risk Level 5. Monte Carlo uncertainty quantification is performed. Decision is recorded as Accepted with assurance level Medium; however, multiple credibility factors show achievedLevel strictly below requiredLevel, including factors assessed at the highest required gradation, which is inconsistent with the declared assurance level.",
