      "rationale": "SST k-omega turbulence model selected based on prior pump literature without sensitivity comparison to alternative turbulence closures. Newtonian blood assumption applied; non-Newtonian sensitivity not evaluated. Hemolysis power-law constants taken from single literature source."
    },
